nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Over my 3NT North has 2 choices. Probably the best bid is 4@H, transfer to spades. And many people don't know this, but 4@C by North in this auction, where partner makes a strong 3NT overcall, is NOT Gerber. It is Stayman.|
